name: Cecil Vane
content:
Cecil Vane was a male Human who operated The Credit Chip casino on Sel Zonn Station during the reign of the Galactic Empire.
A Human business owner, Cecil Vane operated The Credit Chip casino over Brentaal IV. Running a clean business, despite the fact that the house typically received more credits then guests, Vane himself had never been accused of cheating his patrons. All this changed however when the Galactic Empire came to power; After growing unhappy with the Empire's presence, Vane began cheating the casino's Imperial patrons.
